{"tid":850588,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"HK＄700 國產平價手機被發現預載木馬錄音程式","createTime":"2018-10-06T15:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T15:10:31.000Z","uid":51464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc42065d95934ff4340c51fa9f79be8081a959b","tid":850588,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"最近 Bloomberg 報道中，提及到國產伺服器底板被解放軍植入了有如白米般大的迷你惡意程式晶片，能夠打開伺服器「後門」，讓黑客入侵伺服器並竊取資料。事件令到中國所生產的電子產品，包括手機、筆電、伺服器等的產品資訊安全問題再次被受關注。電腦防毒和系統保安產品公司 Sophos，最近發表了研究報告，發現在淘寶上僅售 610 人民幣（折合約 HK$700）的平價《Android 7.0》智能手機，竟然預載了木馬病毒，會將用家的個人資料傳送至特定伺服器。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2176662\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2176662&d=zvjwJMnJdsybTlaoe9kqo2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=dc8cf1ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2176662</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3feaf28b48863661bf574493f0169cc4ed03ef0","tid":850588,"uid":51039,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:24:06.000Z","msg":"要監控都監得柒過人<br />\n人地美帝冇人爆料真係成世都冇人知<br />\n蝗國就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf9bf6839e14be4cdf04b682a7a8e42228160cf","tid":850588,"uid":74361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:57:57.000Z","msg":"S8<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a